We were punished by our own sense of dignity

by our own inability to admit (link-reveal:"inevitable")[(show:?sword)] and total defeat

|sword)[It was like watching a sword slowly being sunk into your chest, millimeter by millimeter, but you refuse to cry out, refuse to whimper or beg for mercy, and there is nothing you can do but watch the metal disappear into your weeping [[flesh->post15-end]].]